relation: Darrow - #50 With great power...comes great backpain. Captain Strong shows his age and the battle comes to an end. Ness, content with his victory, proceeds onto Twoson and the chapter of Onett comes to a close. Also, a cameo by yours truly as the mysterious Check-a-roony guy.
Darrow - #51 Ness travels on his way into Twoson and picks up a new friend in the process: Reginald Jr, the exit mouse.
Darrow - #52 An important call makes its way to Ness in his sleep. Also, exit mouse has both a gambling addiction and a side job of selling faulty rulers.
Darrow - #53 A bike shop that holds...you guessed it, mohawks. Unfortunately, bike riding lessons were not included.
Darrow - #54 After a very short attempt at learning to ride, Ness abandons the bike. Actually, he puts it away in his bag. At just the right angle, it fits perfectly!
